net.opentsdb.query.expression

类 ExpressionDataPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.query.expression.ExpressionDataPoint
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    DataPoint

    public class ExpressionDataPoint
extends Object
implements DataPoint
    Contains the information for a series that has been processed through an expression iterator. Each time a metric data point series set is added we add the metric and compute the tag sets.

    As the iterator progresses, it will call into the reset(long, double) methods.

    从以下版本开始:
    2.3
